The paper discusses the use of Generative Teaching Networks (GTNs) to accelerate learning in AI agents, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the application of GTNs to neural architecture search (NAS), which falls under the sub-category of systems and control (cs.SY).
